B2DBody - Class in box2d
The B2DBody class contains methods and templates for an easy setup process of a Body instance and scanning methods to get its properties.
B2DBody(String) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DBody
Initialises a new B2DBody and sets the default values.
B2DBone - Class in box2d
A B2DBone connects two B2DJoint instances with a rigid B2DBody.
B2DBone(B2DJoint, B2DJoint, int) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DBone
Creates a new B2DBone instance connecting the B2DJoint given.
B2DBoneDir - Enum in box2d
The B2DBoneDir enum is used to specify with which end a certain B2DBone is connected to a B2DMuscle.
B2DBoneDir() - Constructor for enum box2d.B2DBoneDir
 
B2DCamera - Class in box2d
The B2DCamera class is used to convert the Box2D-World coordinates to pixel coordinates and the other way around.
B2DCamera(float, Vec2, Vec2) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DCamera
Initialises a new B2DCamera instance.
B2DJoint - Class in box2d
The B2DJoint class is comparable to a position vector with B2DBone connected to it.
B2DJoint(float[], int) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DJoint
Creates a new B2DJoint within the given bounds minXY_maxXY randomly.
B2DJoint(MutVec2, int) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DJoint
Creates a new B2DJoint from a position given as a MutVec2.
B2DMuscle - Class in box2d
A B2DMuscle sits on a B2DJoint and acts as a "rotation" muscle between two B2DBone instances connected to the B2DJoint.
B2DMuscle(B2DJoint, B2DBone, B2DBone, MutTimer, MutTimer, MutVal, MutVal, int) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DMuscle
Creates a new B2DMuscle with all parameters given.
B2DMuscle(B2DJoint, B2DBone, B2DBone, int) - Constructor for class box2d.B2DMuscle
Creates a new B2DMuscle instance with new references to B2DJoint and B2DBone instances.
